properties.AspNetCoreHostingModel: Indicates whether to run an ASP.NET Core application using IIS in-process or out-of-process.
properties.AspNetCoreModuleName: Indicates which AspNetCoreModule version to use. Versions include V1 and V2.
properties.UserSecretsId: The ID that will be used to locate the file storing secret configuration values for this project at development time.
